oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Words and Music Night - 2016-05-18
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Words and Music Night program held in the CMA Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on May 18, 2016. Hosted by Gary Allan.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Performances include; My Favorite Song (Bob Spanburgh with Jack Clouse and Rovarro Sanders) -- I’ll Stand by You (Misty Rae and Jason Carson with McKenna Rhinehart) -- Which Truck to Choose (Lacey Williams with Hayden Griggs) -- Black and White Towns (Caroline Spence with Skylar Parks) -- Sweet Tennessee (Christy McDonald and Kyle Jones with Hayden Mckee) -- Fall, Fall Down on Me (Trisha Leone with Diego Paz) -- Hey Legs (Shane Adams with Rachel Bowling) -- Stay Strong (Sandy Ramos with AJ Dale) -- Over the Mountains (Kathy Hussey with Nicole Caruso) -- The Music’s Beat (RaShelle Myra with Samantha Jennings) -- I’m Playing Basketball (Deanna Brown with Caleb Justice) -- See the World (Jerry Vandiver with Rory White) -- Nasty Locker Room (Emily Shackelton and Phil Barton with Bailey Brumit and Autumn Burgess) -- Always Headed Your Way (Matt Vrba with Rickia Mitchell) - Lil’ Tennessee Country Boy (Gary Culley with Shaun Groves) -- Another Lover (Tim Buppert with Jeralyn Johnson) -- Her Man ( Gary Allan).
